{"lemma":"مَضِيعَةٍ","slug":"مَضِيعَةٍ","root":"ض.#.ع","root_slug":"ض-_-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-_-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26201"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B6%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26201","headword_ar":"مَضِيعَةٌ","root":"DyE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoyaEapN","text_ar":"مَضْيَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DayaAEN","text_ar":"ضَيَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[an inf. n. of 1, q. v.]. (Mgh, O, Msb, K.) So in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraka EiyaAlahu bimaDiyEapK","text_ar":"تَرَكَ عِيَالَهُ بِمَضِيعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bimaDoyaEapK","text_ar":"بِمَضْيَعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He left his family,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"household, in a state of perishing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (Mgh.) So too in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~aAriqu laA yuqoTaEu fiY maAlK","text_ar":"السَّارِقُ لَا يُقْطَعُ فِى مَالٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bimaDiyEapK","text_ar":"بِمَضِيعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thief shall not suffer amputation"},{"kind":"text","text":"of his hand"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the case of"},{"kind":"text","text":"his stealing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"property in a neglected state"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) And so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa bidaAri maDiyEapK","text_ar":"هُوَ بِدَارِ مَضِيعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * O, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoyaEapK","text_ar":"مَضْيَعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is in a place"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an abode"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of perdition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: or as meaning in this saying,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abandonment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignominy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa muqiymN bidaAri maDiyEapK","text_ar":"هُوَ مُقِيمٌ بِدَارِ مَضِيعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoyaEapK","text_ar":"مَضْيَعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is dwelling in the abode of indolence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his characteristic in his affairs is indolence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  Also, [or perhaps the latter only, as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cause of perishing"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., this latter being app. of the class of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maboxalapN","text_ar":"مَبْخَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majobanapN","text_ar":"مَجْبَنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A desert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waterless desert, that is cut off"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from inhabited regions"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or, as expl. by IJ,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place in which a man perishes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is lost."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}